@startuml
title State diagram for the Plane class

[*] --> Order : Acquire

state "Order" as Order
state "Arrival" as Arrival
state "Preparation" as Preparation
state "Operations" as Operations
state "Maintenance" as Maintenance
state "Dead" as Dead

Order --> Arrival : Delivery

Arrival --> Preparation : Arrival

Preparation --> Operations : Assignment (operations)
Preparation --> Maintenance : Assignment (maintenance)

Operations --> Operations : Scheduled flights

Operations --> Maintenance : No scheduled flights or maintenance required

Maintenance --> Preparation : Servicing

Maintenance --> Dead : Permanently withdrawn from service

Dead --> [*]

@enduml
